 个领域合作清单，希望美方切实认真对待。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-6e036f612ad99ed881bd9ca6a62a6370_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "289 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/542402983"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIpeTow8+d9odMEAMaCDgyODE2MDExIJ25pZYGMBk4kwdABHIJNTQyNDAyOTgzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1657413419.6404638", "card_id": "Q_542402256", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 154}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待安倍枪击案嫌疑人供认称「最初袭击目标并非安倍晋三」? 此供述会影响判决吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据日本广播协会 7 月 9 日报道，嫌疑人山上徹也供认本想袭击宗教团体的干部，但是他无法做到。所以决定袭击日本前首相安倍晋三。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-77f39652f83198005b8240c0c1324073_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "239 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/542402256"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IpeTow8+d9odMEAMaCDgyODE1ODUyIN22pZYGMBc4+ANABXIJNTQyNDAyMjU2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1657413419.6410773", "card_id": "Q_51850049", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 75}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "一次性补交 13 万养老保险划算吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我妈现在 54 岁，现在想一次性补交养老保险（已有农村医保，不含职工医保），总额达到 13W，最初开始拿到 900+ 一月，即交即拿。1 、请问一次性缴纳 13W 费用，多少年回本？ 2 、交了划算吗？ 3 、有更好的商业养老险吗？ 求大神建议。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-ac71c843697e4c6d280768d8d58dfa74_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "215 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/51850049"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IpeTow8+d9